This script targets program coordinators in a system. The program runs to allow various functionalities. 
Coordinators can enter new students into the system. The data is then permanently stored into a text file in the same directory.
Student information include name, midterm grades and final grade. 
There is the feature of finding students by their name.
They can also update the data entered about the students using one of the options.
The program allows users to view the student with highest grades and the lowest grade.
Any student can be deleted from the system. But be sure to make all the necessary changes right before saving the transactions.
